Text: Masterpiece, neat n clean program 4 my windows 7.

Nice program, but you really should have had someone whose native language is English proofread your text.  Some of it is very confusing...if not totally unclear to a native speaker.

On a different matter, do you know how to change a wireless mac address to ANY value in Windows 7.

Before you start telling me how easy it is, try it and see if your changes work.  See if you can connect to a wireless network when you've changed to 00:11:22:33:44:55
